# bias-audit -- Go flagship standard .gitignore (M6 2026-05-27)
# Cohort-port from inception per R174 5-of-5 strict (anchor: canopy).

# Go build artefacts
*.exe
*.exe~
*.dll
*.so
*.dylib
# /bias-audit = root-level build artefact (from `go build .` or
# `go build -o bias-audit ./cmd/bias-audit`); root-anchored so it does
# NOT match the cmd/bias-audit/ source directory.
/bias-audit

# Go test + coverage
*.test
*.out
coverage.txt
coverage.html

# Editor scratch
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
.DS_Store

# Defensive -- no secrets in repo (bias-audit has zero env reads today
# but Phase 2+ tenant-onboarding will introduce credentials; this
# defensive guard ships ahead of that work so a misconfigured local
# .env never lands in version control).
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
